name: Genetic Program - Polynomial Generator
body:
## **Software Engineering Project (University of St Thomas, Fall 2013)**


## Project Description 

A genetic program to find a target solution (x*x -1)/2. The project uses the JGAP framework for implementation.

## Project Members 
* Gandotra, Anshu 
* Misra, Amrit
* Modak, Pradipta
